### Variables
@host = http://localhost:8080
@gameId = {{createGame.response.body.id}}

### 1. Create a New Game
# This will default to Team.DETECTIVE based on your logic
# @name createGame
POST {{host}}/api/games
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. List All Open Games
# Returns games with exactly 1 player waiting
GET {{host}}/api/games
Accept: application/json

### 3. Get a Specific Game by ID
# Uses the ID from the first request if run in order
GET {{host}}/api/game/d30a1c6a-e3d7-4450-beed-510cbd5409a4
Accept: application/json

### 4. Join an Existing Game
# Note: You'll need to provide a valid gameId from the list above
POST {{host}}/api/game/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gameId": "d30a1c6a-e3d7-4450-beed-510cbd5409a4"
}

### 5. Test 404 (Non-existent Game)
GET {{host}}/api/game/non-existent-uuid-123